race.description: 2025 Holdfast Insurance Brokers Gawler Cup Hcp
race.comment: Terrific content for the feature race. DUAL PRESSURE (10) carried a big weight to score at Murray Bridge on Cup day. Faces a tougher field but will relish the weight drop and is expected to take catching. CHICAGO STORM (3) beat a few of these last time when resuming from a spell and can only be fitter. Unbeaten on this circuit and worth following up. EASY CAMPESE (8) staked the pace and won on the Parks track last time. This is richer but he is very well weighted with the claim. Can give a sight here. AIR ASSAULT (2) is Group 1 placed earlier in the career and has a bit on these in ability. Began this campaign in stakes class at Flemington so will relish the drop back to this level second-up. Big improver.
